> Please perform a comprehensive audit of the Python test suite in this repository. Your analysis should:

1. First, explore the entire test directory structure to understand what tests exist
2. Read and analyze each test file in detail
3. Evaluate tests based on these principles:
   - Do tests actually test real functionality vs just mocking everything?
